Source.Name: canta-gtk-theme
Source.Summary: Canta is a flat Material Design theme.
Source.Description: Canta is a flat Material Design theme for GTK 3, GTK 2 and Gnome-Shell which supports GTK 3 and GTK 2 based desktop environments like Gnome, Unity, Budgie, Pantheon, XFCE, Mate, etc.
